<!--
	HHS Create Lookup_Lists.xml
	
	This file is used to create the common Lookup lists that are
	used in a HHS (crhodes) style SharePoint Site Collection.
	The Lookup lists provide values to several HHS_SiteColumns.
	
	NB. It is not possible to specify the Id of a list.  The SiteColumns
		need to query the web for the Id of a lookup list.
	
	Population of the lists is done by a corresponding file,
	HHS Populate Lookup_Lists.xml
	-->
